Actions.Text: tell application "System Events"	tell application process "HazelHelper"		tell menu bar 2			tell menu bar item 1				try					with timeout of 0.1 seconds						perform action "AXPress"					end timeout				end try			end tell		end tell	end tellend telldo shell script "killall 'System Events'"tell application "System Events"	repeat 2 times		key code 125	end repeat	delay 0.2	key code 124	delay 1	key code 36end tell
